# Orca developer block

- Site-scoped block: APIs/actions/theme belong to the current Orca site. Cross-site reuse = re-upload the ZIP.
- Allowlisted imports only: `react`, `react-dom`, `@orca/blocks`, `clsx`, `zod`.
- Prefer `var(--theme-font-*)` and semantic colors (`hsl(var(--primary))`) with `context:theme`.
- Keep root background transparent unless you intentionally draw a card.
- Pack with `pnpm zip` only (excludes `sdk/`, `preview/`, `.cursor/`, agent docs).
- Do not bake site fonts into the ZIP; runtime bridge injects Appearance fonts.
